        "content": "## 📧 AI Email Manager Tutorial\n\nThis workflow teaches you how to build an AI agent that can:\n✅ Read your emails\n✅ Send new emails\n✅ Remember conversation context\n\n**How it works:**\n1. Chat Trigger - Opens a chat interface\n2. AI Agent - Understands your requests\n3. Gmail Tools - Read and send emails\n4. Memory - Remembers your conversation",
        "color": 4
      },
